We have investigated on the Javascript error blocking the rendering.
Everyhting is in "auiplugin-5.6.7-jira-1.jar" in the file "tabs.js";
We have replaced a single line of this javascript to make usable JIRA for our users (IE8 and the others).

{code:title=tabs.js|borderStyle=solid}
280 : tabs.forEach(function (tab) {
281 : calculateResponsiveTabs(tab, i);
{code}

Becomes : 
{code:title=tabs.js|borderStyle=solid}
280 : $.each(tabs, function (index, tab) {
281 : calculateResponsiveTabs(tab, index);
{code}

